Title: Emergency First Aid
Description:
We have to patch everyone up before we can begin the search for my... for the missing expedition.

Take this first aid kit and tend to the wounded. No one gets left behind.
ObjectivesText: Use a First Aid Kit on Austin Huxworth, Bjorn Stouthands, and Kee-la.
RewardText: We're ready to move. Let's find that missing expedition.

Objectives.Text: First Aid Kit used on Bjorn Stouthands
First Aid Kit used on Kee-La
First Aid Kit used on Austin Huxworth
